A teenage girl who was kicked in the face and beaten by a student in her class has been suspended despite the vicious attack being caught on camera.

Fellow students at the Texas school filmed the moment the teenager was punched and kicked to the ground in her classroom.

But when her father contacted the Harris County school he was told his daughter was to be suspended along with her attacker. 

